Reason: When the JointOfSpace+forall precondition on pick is active (case 5, fridge items),
PDDLStream passes AtPosition fluents with UniqueOptValue for door joints that haven't been
sampled yet during optimistic planning. Calling p.assign() on UniqueOptValue crashes.
Same guard already exists for ataconf at lines 1260-1267.

